  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic and red onion, sauté for about 2 minutes until softened.",
    "Include celery sticks and cook for another minute. Add baby pak kai and stir-fry together for 1-2 more minutes.",
    "Drizzle tangy sauce evenly over the vegetables in the wok, ensuring all ingredients are well-coated.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds on top of the dish and finish with a few thyme leaves for garnish.",
    "Taste and adjust salt level if necessary. Serve hot."
